{"tid":2241680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國政府網站禁香港瀏覽 勞工、人口普查局已封鎖","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T16:33:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"60910788d695551e18f01ad77403d735c312f316","tid":2241680,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"香港享有資訊自由流通的獨特性，但據英國《金融時報》報道，美國多月來已封鎖香港市民瀏覽美國勞工統計局（Bureau of Labor Statistics）及美國人口普查局（US Census Bureau）的網站。報道亦引述一位美國官員，預期華府不再視香港為中國的自治地區，未來會有更多美國政府網站禁止香港市民瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/10/13/us-government-website/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F10%2F13%2Fus-government-website%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=3459a53b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/10/13/us-government-website/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"3cdefb5823ccabda0f91e167797ac6e3d4173bb3","tid":2241680,"uid":100581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"N咁耐啦<br />\n不過依家先上報姐<br />\n仲有，依家 <span class=\"red\">.mil </span>既網站已經唔係成日成功access 到"},{"pid":"7c859bb1e7b648f969334d71fe3214a5998c3f2a","tid":2241680,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"一早用緊VPN<br />\n不過好慢"},{"pid":"7a80196cbe6f23dead183d16fbfac191c35eb5eb","tid":2241680,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3dc9e7aa012fcd54400404873e6377460e2b2a","tid":2241680,"uid":23445,"like":0,"di